{
  "id": "RAW_91baa090",
  "title": "【第 3611 期】优化网页字体",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&mid=2651277889&idx=1&sn=15b1ef41021b7f6c98ebffb6fd688113",
  "date": "2025-11-11 05:30:00",
  "author": "前端早读课",
  "siteName": "前端早读课",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3bb55374&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FmeG6Vo0MevjeJEib9OITicAur0UIhibjIA0yWznSAOqmTQzM0P00XadRiaaUXOt4BfUo7XJPoBQMea5Pb43jJ4pCHg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px !important;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">前言</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">匆匆忙忙刚刚赶回来；探讨了如何优化网页字体以提升网页性能。今日前端早读课文章由 @Lucas Dohmen 分享，@飘飘编译。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">译文从这开始～～</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">字体是网页性能中非常关键的一环：自定义字体可能导致明显的布局偏移，并且文件体积往往相当庞大。最快的解决方式是完全避免使用它们，直接采用系统安全字体（web-safe fonts）。然而，自定义字体能赋予网站独特的风格，因此许多网页设计师仍认为它们不可或缺。那么，怎样才能让字体尽可能小，从而减少对网页性能的影响呢？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651276936&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=7aa45eb5f2c6b3314371b14ccc348820&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【第3550期】盘点字体性能优化方案\" data-itemshowtype=\"11\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【第3550期】盘点字体性能优化方案</a></span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">字体类型（Typefaces）</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">以我在本网站使用的 Fixel 字体为例。Fixel 提供三种版本：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;padding-left:2em;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">用于标题的显示字体（display variant）</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0.25em;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">用于正文的文本字体（text variant）</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0.25em;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">可变字体（variable font）</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">无论是文本版和显示版各包含 9 种字重，并分别有斜体与常规体。正确地说，Fixel Display 字体族包含 18 个字体文件（如 FixelDisplay-Bold.otf）。而可变字体只用一个文件就能覆盖全部字重范围 —— 听起来很棒，但代价是文件体积更大。显示版和文本版的每个字体文件大约为 120–140 kB，而可变字体则达到 470 kB。</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">压缩（Compression）</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们能做的第一步优化是对字体进行压缩。常用的格式是 WOFF2，它其实就是用 Brotli 压缩过的 OTF 或 TTF 文件。来看下压缩前后的大小对比：</span></p>\n  <table style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-spacing:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;width:360px;margin-bottom:16px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <thead>\n    <tr style=\"border-top:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);box-sizing:border-box;\">\n     <th style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;font-weight: bold;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">字体</span></p>\n     </th>\n     <th style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;font-weight: bold;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">未压缩大小</span></p>\n     </th>\n     <th style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;font-weight: bold;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">压缩后大小</span></p>\n     </th>\n    </tr>\n   </thead>\n   <tbody>\n    <tr style=\"border-top:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);box-sizing:border-box;\">\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">Fixel Text Medium</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">138 kB</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">74 kB</span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr style=\"border-top:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);box-sizing:border-box;\">\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">Fixel Variable</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">472 kB</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">199 kB</span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">压缩对可变字体的效果尤其显著。因此，如果你打算在网站中使用三种或更多这种字体，采用可变字体会更合适。不过，这只是优化的起点。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651274260&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=02eeed90e4a91745f63d13215773b425&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【第3420期】字体性能优化终极指南\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【第3420期】字体性能优化终极指南</a></span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">字符子集化（Subsetting）</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">从概念上讲，一个字体文件会将每个字符映射到对应的字形。一个字体通常包含大量在网站中根本不会用到的字符。以 Fixel 为例，它同时包含拉丁字母和西里尔字母。这对支持英语和乌克兰语的网站来说非常棒，但对仅使用英语或德语的网站而言，这些多余的字符就是优化的空间。Fixel 的每个字体大约包含 600 个符号，我们可以只保留需要的部分，这个过程就叫 子集化（subsetting）。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们可以使用基于 Python 的工具 fonttools 来实现。如果你已安装 Python 和 pip，可以这样安装：</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;pip install fonttools brotli uharfbuzz</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">或者，也可以使用我准备好的 Dockerfile：<a href=\"https://codeberg.org/moonglum/compress/src/branch/main/fonts\" target=\"_blank\">https://codeberg.org/moonglum/compress/src/branch/main/fonts</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">接着，我们要通过 Unicode 编码或编码范围指定所需字符。本网站主要使用英语和德语，因此可以先保留 94 个可打印的 ASCII 字符（范围 0000–007F），这些涵盖了英语所需的全部字母、常用标点（如&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></code><span leaf=\"\">）以及数学符号（如&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">+</span></code><span leaf=\"\">）。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">德语还需额外保留大小写的三个变音字母和小写的 ß（Eszett）：</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;00C4, 00D6, 00DC, 00DF, 00E4, 00F6, 00FC</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，还有一些其他常见字符：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;padding-left:2em;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">引号：如果不想用 ASCII 引号，我们应加入语言特定的排版引号，如英文&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">“ ”</span></code><span leaf=\"\">（201C, 201D）和德文&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">„ “</span></code><span leaf=\"\">（201E, 201F）</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0.25em;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">乘号与除号：</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">×</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;和&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">÷</span></code><span leaf=\"\">（00D7, 00F7）</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0.25em;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">短破折号与长破折号：</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">–</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;和&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">-</span></code><span leaf=\"\">（2013, 2014）</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0.25em;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">撇号与省略号：</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">’</span></code><span leaf=\"\">（2019）和&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">…</span></code><span leaf=\"\">（2026）</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果忘记某个字符会怎样？浏览器会按&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">font-family: Fixel, system-ui</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;的顺序回退到下一个字体。虽然能正常显示，但排版效果可能会很奇怪。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503794218\" data-ratio=\"0.2683982683982684\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"231\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4ca4e683&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FmeG6Vo0MevhKdNqp2KbqhG65SZYribUlFW7LAmv4bq2L0shnt0e1kl6EPKHw6ymlrNsXeBmerUpNINr4NB3hJ8Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在确定字符范围后，我们用 fonttools 对字体进行子集化和压缩（生成 WOFF2）：</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;compress-fonts fonttools subset\\</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;--unicodes=\"0000-007F,00C4,00D6,00DC,00DF,00E4,00F6,00FC,201C,201D,201E,201C,00D7,00F7,2013,2014,2019,2026\"\\</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;--layout-features=\"*\"\\</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;--flavor=woff2\\</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;FixelText-Medium.otf</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">子集化后的结果如下：</span></p>\n  <table style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-spacing:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;width:360px;margin-bottom:16px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <thead>\n    <tr style=\"border-top:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);box-sizing:border-box;\">\n     <th style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;font-weight: bold;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">字体</span></p>\n     </th>\n     <th style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;font-weight: bold;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">未压缩大小</span></p>\n     </th>\n     <th style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;font-weight: bold;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">压缩后大小</span></p>\n     </th>\n     <th style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;font-weight: bold;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">子集化后</span></p>\n     </th>\n    </tr>\n   </thead>\n   <tbody>\n    <tr style=\"border-top:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);box-sizing:border-box;\">\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">Fixel Text Medium</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">138 kB</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">74 kB</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">29 kB</span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr style=\"border-top:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);box-sizing:border-box;\">\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">Fixel Variable</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">472 kB</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">199 kB</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">74 kB</span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">排版特性（Typographic Features）</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">现代字体支持许多排版特性，这远超本文的范围。fonttools 可以移除部分特性，并默认保留一组实用的功能，比如 连字（ligatures）—— 如果字体支持，浏览器会自动启用。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651270628&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b2f1d2434e69554931eb6e45adaeef39&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【第3258期】Font2svg 特殊字体渲染方案\" data-itemshowtype=\"11\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【第3258期】Font2svg 特殊字体渲染方案</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">前面我们使用&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">--layout-features=\"*\"</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;指令保留了所有特性。若移除此选项，文件体积还能大幅下降：</span></p>\n  <table style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-spacing:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;width:360px;margin-bottom:16px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <thead>\n    <tr style=\"border-top:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);box-sizing:border-box;\">\n     <th style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;font-weight: bold;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">字体</span></p>\n     </th>\n     <th style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;font-weight: bold;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">未压缩大小</span></p>\n     </th>\n     <th style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;font-weight: bold;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">压缩后大小</span></p>\n     </th>\n     <th style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;font-weight: bold;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">子集化后</span></p>\n     </th>\n     <th style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;font-weight: bold;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">特性精简后</span></p>\n     </th>\n    </tr>\n   </thead>\n   <tbody>\n    <tr style=\"border-top:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);box-sizing:border-box;\">\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">Fixel Text Medium</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">138 kB</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">74 kB</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">29 kB</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">11 kB</span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr style=\"border-top:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);box-sizing:border-box;\">\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">Fixel Variable</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">472 kB</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">199 kB</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">74 kB</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 6px 13px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">31 kB</span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">总结（Conclusion）</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文展示了如何大幅缩小自定义网页字体的体积，并比较了可变字体与非可变字体的差异。在本例中，可变字体约为非可变字体的三倍大。因此，只有在需要使用两种以上字体变体（如不同字重或斜体 / 非斜体组合）时，才值得使用可变字体。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"mp_common_product_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-product data-windowproduct=\"v1=HME-g_t-c__Dr4QPqBa96kILtcX9LIUslt4yVGMyYPVZqlfR1T8WMmKFf0G_LaG1bWlxCGXNvpTkxw\" data-cardtype=\"1\" data-title=\"【官方正版】如何高效远程工作\" data-type=\"0\"></mp-common-product></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:0px !important;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">关于本文</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">译者：@飘飘</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">作者：@Lucas Dohmen</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">原文：<a href=\"https://lucas.dohmen.io/posts/2025/10/20/webfonts/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lucas.dohmen.io/posts/2025/10/20/webfonts/</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章深入探讨了通过 WOFF2 压缩、字符子集化和排版特性精简等方法，优化网页字体以显著提升前端性能的实践指南。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章深入探讨了通过 WOFF2 压缩、字符子集化和排版特性精简等方法，优化网页字体以显著提升前端性能的实践指南。",
  "summary": "本文详细阐述了网页字体优化对于提升网站性能的重要性与具体实践方案。文章首先指出自定义字体可能导致布局偏移和文件体积庞大，随后介绍了三种核心优化策略：首先是字体压缩，通过 WOFF2 格式将字体文件显著缩小，并对比了压缩前后可变字体与非可变字体的效果；其次是字符子集化，利用 fonttools 工具移除字体中不常用的字符（如多余语言的字符集），大幅削减文件大小，并强调了精细配置字符范围以避免排版回退的重要性；最后是排版特性精简，通过移除不必要的 OpenType 特性进一步优化字体体积。文章还对比分析了可变字体与非可变字体的优劣，指出可变字体仅在需要两种以上字体变体时才具备性能优势。整体而言，文章提供了一套实用且可操作的字体优化方法，对前端开发者具有重要的实践指导价值。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "字体压缩（WOFF2）是优化体积的首要且高效手段",
      "explanation": "通过将 OTF/TTF 文件压缩为 WOFF2 格式，能显著减小字体文件大小，尤其对可变字体效果更佳，是基础且必要的优化步骤。"
    },
    {
      "point": "字符子集化能大幅削减字体体积，但需精细配置以防回退问题",
      "explanation": "移除不常用字符（如多余语言字符）可将字体文件进一步缩小，但需确保包含所有必需的 Unicode 字符和排版符号，以避免字体回退导致排版异常。"
    },
    {
      "point": "合理管理排版特性可进一步优化字体大小并平衡功能需求",
      "explanation": "移除不必要的 OpenType 特性（如不常用的连字）能进一步减小字体体积，需权衡文件大小与排版效果，以达到最佳性能与视觉平衡。"
    },
    {
      "point": "可变字体仅在需要多种字重或样式时才具备性能优势",
      "explanation": "尽管可变字体单个文件能覆盖所有字重，但其基准体积较大，只有在网站使用两种以上字体变体时，其性能优势才能显现，需根据实际需求选择。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "自定义字体可能导致明显的布局偏移，并且文件体积往往相当庞大。",
    "压缩对可变字体的效果尤其显著。因此，如果你打算在网站中使用三种或更多这种字体，采用可变字体会更合适。",
    "一个字体通常包含大量在网站中根本不会用到的字符。以 Fixel 为例，它同时包含拉丁字母和西里尔字母。",
    "如果忘记某个字符会怎样？浏览器会按 font-family: Fixel， system-ui 的顺序回退到下一个字体。虽然能正常显示，但排版效果可能会很奇怪。",
    "在本例中，可变字体约为非可变字体的三倍大。因此，只有在需要使用两种以上字体变体（如不同字重或斜体 / 非斜体组合）时，才值得使用可变字体。"
  ],
